{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"20376-eu-consigo-desenhar-coisas","title":"Eu consigo desenhar coisas!","description":"Crianças podem fazer v´árias coisas legais. Quais são elas?","language":"Portuguese","langCode":"pt","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Juliana Arai"],"illustrators":["Tanvee Nabar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/20376-eu-consigo-desenhar-coisas"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/709183/size3/68acc59fc68640e3cabffa2a367a7375.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/709183/size6/68acc59fc68640e3cabffa2a367a7375.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10628/size6/f182a1c235e0c8a7a9578f3d63a301d4.jpg","text":"Eu sou um menino crescido agora.\nEu consigo desenhar e fazer coisas.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10630/size6/8f4085b833328ebad0bb4c829d6bc3bd.jpg","text":"Eu desenho minha mãe, ela posa para mim.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10631/size6/9a216827141b6e2e9285e866397d659d.jpg","text":"Eu desenho a minha irmã, mas ela não posa para mim.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10632/size6/3feaf340a7b0144fd6cd477eac36444e.jpg","text":"Eu desenho muitas coisas.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10633/size6/57aef08a63fdae439e3d9d81f2d5f94c.jpg","text":"Mas não me deixam desenhar na parede.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10634/size6/53110634399378d31dd1fe12d51e871a.jpg","text":"Eu faço coisas.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10635/size6/73cd6940cf5301f73dd47e6f6cb05a7d.jpg","text":"Eu faço o desenho de uma gata, ela é gordinha.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10636/size6/534ba0193961d8a8422ee4cf809b86e3.jpg","text":"Eu faço um peixe. Ele é pequeno.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10637/size6/fe3687fb06f0fefba37c63c2b330ca2c.jpg","text":"Eu faço barquinhos de papel, passarinhos e aviões.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10638/size6/47a6a033579def00aaa02baebd79c105.jpg","text":"Eu faço casas e trens.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10639/size6/d5faf2ebda41b84ac55199ff36d2e935.jpg","text":"Minha irmã faz uma bagunça!\nEu faço muitas coisas, mas a minha irmã pequena ainda não.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":91}}